## Why This Is Asked
This probes practical data governance, real-time-to-batch pipelines, and DR considerations in Azure for large-scale workloads.

## Key Concepts
- Event Hubs ingestion and Spark Structured Streaming
- Delta Lake with schema drift handling
- PII masking at ingestion
- Purview lineage and data residency compliance
- Cross-region DR and serverless analytics

## Code Example
```javascript
// PII masking pseudo-code
function maskPII(record) {
  if (!record?.email) return record;
  record.email = record.email.replace(/[^@]+@/, '*****@');
  return record;
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you validate end-to-end lineage across regions?
- What are failure modes in cross-region DR and mitigations?
